cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The challenge focuses on activity recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): Many of the challenge participants used machine learning techniques to develop their models. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The dataset used in the challenge consists of videos, which falls under the multimedia category. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): Some of the challenge participants used text-based information retrieval techniques to improve their models. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): Some of the challenge participants used natural language processing techniques to improve their models.
